---
// Case Studies component showcasing our work
---

<section id="case-studies" class="case-studies">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2>Case Studies</h2>
    <p class="section-description">See how we've helped organizations achieve their goals and create meaningful impact.</p>
    
    <div class="case-studies-grid">
      <article class="case-study">
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <h3>Tech Startup Growth</h3>
          <p>Helped a promising tech startup scale from 10 to 100 employees while maintaining their innovative culture and mission.</p>
          <div class="case-study-metrics">
            <span class="metric highlight">300% Growth</span>
            <span class="metric highlight">18 Months</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      
      <article class="case-study">
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <h3>Non-Profit Transformation</h3>
          <p>Guided a non-profit organization through a complete digital transformation, increasing their reach by 500%.</p>
          <div class="case-study-metrics">
            <span class="metric highlight">500% Reach</span>
            <span class="metric highlight">12 Months</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      
      <article class="case-study">
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <h3>Corporate Innovation</h3>
          <p>Facilitated innovation workshops for a Fortune 500 company, resulting in 15 new product concepts and improved team collaboration.</p>
          <div class="case-study-metrics">
            <span class="metric highlight">15 Concepts</span>
            <span class="metric highlight">6 Months</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .case-studies {
    background-color: var(--bg-light);
  }

  .case-studies h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .case-studies-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .case-study {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .case-study:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .case-study h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .case-study p {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .case-study-metrics {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .metric {
    background: var(--bg-light);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .metric.highlight {
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .case-studies h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .case-studies-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .case-study {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .case-study h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .case-study-metrics {
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .metric {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
